# One component per file

## Rules

- Maximum **1 exported React component** per file under `src/`.
- No inline or anonymous components inside other components (including `ReactMarkdown` `components` maps).
- Barrel `index.ts` files may **re-export only** — never define components there.
- File name must match the component name in PascalCase (e.g. `HeroSection.tsx` → `HeroSection`).

## Exceptions

- Next.js route files (`page.tsx`, `layout.tsx`) keep their framework exports (`default`, `generateMetadata`, etc.).
- Pure utility modules with no React components are unaffected.
